{"type": "article", "id": 34161, "title": "用针线缝出你在这个星球走过的路，如何？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-11-06T23:04:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 28155, "name": "Claesson Koivisto Rune"}, {"id": 34646, "name": "Suck UK"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 136, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161106203349nUmGO34IQPYKFf2w.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Soft Stone by Claesson Koivisto Rune</h3><p>在海水冲刷的作用下，沙滩石坚硬又光滑的触感摸上去给人一种舒适的感觉。受到这种大自然的启发，瑞典工作室 <a href=\"http://www.claessonkoivistorune.se/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Claesson Koivisto Rune</a> 耗时两年打造了名为 Soft Stone 的电子颈肩枕。优雅的灰色鹅卵石造型挑战了传统的颈肩枕设计，能够更好地融入居家环境当中，弱化了物件的突兀感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170356qtKOJwHAD6r5FUIm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.691932\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170356wyBJpCX3fk1z5AG9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016110617035728GqawgEOdcsxWmL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170356ph3tWSzmI9cvgBnw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>FLAX by Christien Meindertsma</h3><p>随着环保意识的增强，越来越多的设计师也开始探索可降解制品的未来，试着让那些被低估的材料能够重获新生。今年荷兰设计周的产品设计类获奖作品就是 <a href=\"http://www.christienmeindertsma.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Christien Meindertsma</a> 设计的可降解座椅 FLAX。Meindertsma 一直在进行对于亚麻潜能的研究，在设计公司 <a href=\"http://www.labelbreed.nl/\" rel=\"nofollow\">LABEL/BREED</a> 和纤维公司 <a href=\"http://www.enkev.com/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Enkev</a> 的帮助下，亚麻同天然羊毛以及强力的生物塑料纤维结合后通过热压成为了可塑性极强而且几乎不产生肥料的新型材质。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170427CtI27hmRY1zSJVw0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170426KZWEGelIhsAiQkOS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611061704260EYsj1IRczdX8hP2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016110617042704lWYzatCc92AKSv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>Float Shelf by PRISM Designs</h3><p>如果你有一台 iMac 而且发现桌上东西有点多，PRISM Designs 带来的这款 Float 置物搁板提供了一个不会显得突兀的解决办法。这张纤薄的搁板由一整块实铝加工而成，和 iMac 的搭配看上去非常自然。它最高可以承重 4.5 千克的重量，应对一些日常的收纳需要绰绰有余。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/hand/float-shelfthe-ultimate-shelf-for-tapered-edge-ima\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 75 美元。</p><p><br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106211552RdhlQfZLKcM7DePs.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561514\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611062115527VRLdoeGu51UXiQY.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561514\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106211553lu7r2AC9QFaXJGVZ.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714706\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106211552rvaWCT6IUNh7894d.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561514\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106211553ZMmbnPAqGsDtR2Ik.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Elos Skateboard by Elos</h3><p>为了解决通勤路上最后几公里的问题，四位在美国求学的台湾学生集结在了一起，凭借对滑板的喜爱，研发了一款名为 Elos 的滑板。和强调个性化的街头风不同的是，这块不依靠电力驱动的小滑板还是围绕着“在城市中轻松滑行”的概念设计的。特别设计的脚钉能够更好地应对斜坡，两公斤左右的小身材携带起来相当方便。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/winstonian/elos-the-first-and-only-urban-lifestyle-skateboard\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 129 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170451Xj0IykwCtzvusO6P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.520588\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170451Z3KXLtT8imIgGJHY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.525000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170452jaS7Td9uDZGoE3tI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.523529\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170452znbPFpIa1QZSV0Rd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.525000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170452i70XJKBFp61L89EY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.807353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Cross Stitch Map by Suck UK</h3><p>旅行归来，除了手帐和各类纪念品之外还有很多记录回忆的方法。如果你更喜欢亲自动手，英国品牌 <a href=\"http://www.suck.uk.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Suck UK</a> 推出的这份世界地图可以让你用针线描绘足迹。虽然概念本身并不新奇，但已经设计好等你缝制的地图要比从零开始方便了不少，剩下的就看你自己的创意了。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/B01EHO8394/om-btm-20/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 32.76 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611061705096f8YI2dB3VKra1vC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170508xGRZaluBPMyg6LKU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170508QpndhIGfmriw4zFW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170508sEhoCf1HAP30TZL9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170508gBvnwS2xslkLREVP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170508RZxE1pUmOyANLej7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Promenade by Isabel Tabarini et al.</h3><p>喜欢城市又喜欢巧克力？由三位包装设计学生带来的概念巧克力 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/38798761/PROMENADE-CHOCOLATIERS\" rel=\"nofollow\">Promenade</a> 是一件有着简洁美而且非常注重细节的作品。以巴塞罗那的城市风光为核心，不光是包装上精美的插画，连巧克力都塑成了对应建筑物的造型。盒子由一个纯色纸销固定，翻开后可以在背面发现建筑位置、建成年份等基本信息。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170551TFwlSR2WNxG18Vvq.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170555shYE8TZt5P64OADK.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611061705582yP5UDSoFOEg3lXT.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170557YyI4BMKTHFctO19J.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170556G6klmj31boKPvFIr.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161106170558I5BHND3YMdpg9kxZ.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.690000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}